{"tid":2019842,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[17/5行動post] 振興藍色經濟行動，”真。幫襯”藍店","createTime":"2020-05-16T14:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T02:12:48.000Z","uid":134093,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"55ce0c47cea2b3c3a558bdc3c28023377b6a7eda","tid":2019842,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:33:55.000Z","msg":"地點: 照舊<br />\n時間: 1400<br />\n<br />\ntg: 用開果個<br />\n<br />\n內容: 黑暴破壞香港經濟，是次活動旨在振興經濟，香港再出發！<br />\n我哋藍店最和諧，歡迎大家入內坐低<br />\n我知道好多人有經濟困難，食嘢幫襯係其次<br />\n最緊要人到，齋坐都無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尤其係美心呢d大集團，心繫香港，服務社會<br />\n元氣飲茶食薑一律免費！<br />\n希望有更加多藍店可以效法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為防暴徒入內破壞，如果見到任何可疑人物<br />\n請立即報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711055bc146c9a6569af029398e1b3d45c11e808","tid":2019842,"uid":197939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:35:01.000Z","msg":"推比民陣睇！想反國歌法嘅入尼！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2019775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2019775</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cd5a71ef3efddd65916ee5ecabf09b069618d0a7","tid":2019842,"uid":134093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:35:10.000Z","msg":"飲茶！<br />\n食薑！"},{"pid":"a53d43f5ac95f522b127af0675c9c3c62fb6f2c2","tid":2019842,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:35:23.000Z","msg":"飲茶！<br />\n食薑！"},{"pid":"fc7d5ca5020b52365e58cf396c865a0c6daf8d5b","tid":2019842,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286fc857d852895b98903b6ee83646554cd1733f","tid":2019842,"uid":198181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:37:13.000Z","m